    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EPA 试图收回 200 亿美元气候法拨款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/epa-seeking-to-claw-back-20-billion-in-awards-from-climate-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国环境保护署署长李·泽尔丁周三晚间表示，该署将试图收回根据总统乔·拜登签署的气候法授予的约 200 亿美元气候项目资金，并称这项努力是一项没有适当监督的“计划”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/epa-seeking-to-claw-back-20-billion-in-awards-from-climate-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 04:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国起诉纽约非法移民身份证法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府正在就 2019 年的一项法律对纽约州提起诉讼，该法律允许无证移民获得州身份证明，同时向联邦当局保密他们的数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可以将墨西哥湾更名为美国湾吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-will-change-the-name-of-the-gulf-of-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——四个多世纪以来，从佛罗里达州到德克萨斯州再到墨西哥的这片水域一直被称为墨西哥湾。但几周后，唐纳德·特朗普总统和白宫官员试图改写地图，将其称为美国湾——并坚持要求其他人也这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-will-change-the-name-of-the-gulf-of-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 19:36:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
